Package: OmicsLens
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Omics Integration Pipeline with Interactive Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-20
Authors@R: person("Priyansh", "Pathak",
    email = "priyanshpt84@gmail.com",
    role  = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: An end-to-end multi-omics integration pipeline that combines
    RNA-Seq, whole-genome sequencing (WGS), and DNA methylation data through
    MOFA2 latent factor analysis. OmicsLens provides an accessible interface
    for wet-lab scientists to perform multi-omics integration, differential
    expression analysis, gene set enrichment analysis (GSEA), differentially
    methylated region (DMR) calling, and survival analysis. Results are
    explored through an interactive Shiny dashboard and exported as
    reproducible HTML reports. Unlike existing tools, OmicsLens wraps the
    full MOFA2 workflow behind a single five-function API designed for
    non-computational biologists.
